<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.4.8">
<l>unta maṭikaḷ muṉiva ruṉṉainā ṉeṉkaiyiṟ kōlāl</l>
<l>nonti ṭamōtavuṅ killēṉ nuṅkaḷta māni raiyellām</l>
<l>vantu pukutarum pōtu vāṉiṭait teyvaṅkaḷ kāṇa</l>
<l>vanti yampōtaṅku nillē lāḻiyaṅ kaiyaṉē vārāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Your father will be angry; I am not able to really hurt you, even though</l>
<l>I beat [you] with a stick in my hand. When your whole cowherd</l>
<l>Comes and enters [the village], don’t stand there at twilight time</l>
<l>So that spirits in mid-air can see! You with a discus in hand, come!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
